  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Corneal Cross Linking in&#xD;
      a Continuous Beam versus Pulsed Treatments across epithelium on and epithelium off surfaces.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
